    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After a few-- few weeks we were there, we learned [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or, [NON-ENGLISH], it was running, you know, all the things [INAUDIBLE].",
